it.unicam.cs.bdslab.aspralign

Class ArcAnnotatedSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unicam.cs.bdslab.aspralign.ArcAnnotatedSequence

  • public class ArcAnnotatedSequence
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of an RNA secondary structure with any kind of pseudoknot. It consists of the nucleotide primary sequence and of a list of weak bonds given as pairs of positions in the primary sequence. Positions start at 1 and end at the length of the primary sequence.
    Author:
    Luca Tesei
